      <div class="sectionDiv chart">
        <div class="chart-explanation" data-aos="fade">
          <h1>Impact from various Ethnic groups</h1>
          <p>
            This graph shows the contribution of various ethnic groups towards
            medical inadherence. Graph is scaled down to represent the number of
            patients who didn't adhered to the medication out of every 100
            patients of that ethinicity.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="chart-itself" data-aos="fade">
          <canvas id="raceChart"></canvas>
