      <div class="sectionDiv chart">
        <div class="chart-explanation" data-aos="fade">
          <h1>Which ages contribute the most?</h1>
          <p>
            This graph compares the number of people who dropped their
            medication before time and thir ages. The graph clearly shows that
            young-aged people (24-40 years) are highest contributors. This can
            be attributed to the fast paced lifestyle and negligence towards
            health of youth.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="chart-itself" data-aos="fade">
