            medical defaulters, with no one even near it.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="chart-itself" data-aos="fade">
          <canvas id="cityChart"></canvas>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="sectionDiv chart">
        <div class="chart-explanation" data-aos="fade">
          <h1>Gender Factor</h1>
          <p>
            This doughnut chart shows the distribution of defaulters on basis of
            gender. The readings show that women have a higher rate of leaving
            medication before the prescribed time as compared to men.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="chart-itself gender-chart-itself" data-aos="fade">
